title: Taylor Wilderness Research Station Archives
paragraph: The Taylor Wilderness Research Station Archive features video interviews, archival documents, artifacts, research outputs, and other photographs and ephemera collected from those who have made Taylor the unique and transformative place it's been for over 40 years.
